---
title: Smoked Salmon Breakfast Sammies Serves 2 | with Chive Cream Cheese and Fried Eggs
description: Forget the bacon, we've topped this morning breakfast sandwich with smoked salmon and freshly cracked egg! Chive cream cheese is the perfect spread for this sammie!
